         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">… ¶ In case you should like to keep  ¶ to ¶  Todea please do so — I am not in want of this plant, — as I bought the other day in Ghent at Lindens 5 big Balantiums and 3 nice Todeas in splendid conditi...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="Progress%20note"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; color: #ff0000; "
               xml:lang="en">Image of complete letter needed</p>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">M73.04.26</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">John Booth to Joseph Hooker</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew, Directors' correspondence, vol. 135, f. 249.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">…</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">In case you should like to keep <seg style="background-color: #ffff00; ">to</seg> Todea please do so — I am not in want of this plant, — as I bought the other day in Ghent at Lindens 5 big Balantiums and 3 nice Todeas in splendid condition for 1300 francs[.]<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Editorial addition</p>
               </note> I want to form a group of them in my grand house in Berlin, – it will be something extraordinary. — Instead of the Todea you may find something else, – only no Orchids. Are you going to Vienna? and which way do you take in case you go?</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am, with kindest regards to Mrs Hooker from Mrs Booth and myself</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Ever sincerely yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">John Booth</hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
